cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.RO

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formal language (LTL) to specify behavioral properties of systems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with autonomous systems and synthesizing controllers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with designing controllers that conform to given correctness properties. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper proposes a novel maximum satisfiability encoding for the search for an optimal implementation. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with autonomous systems and controllers.
